<h1>About CampusFix</h1>
<p>CampusFix demonstrates a realistic ASP.NET Core MVC application using C#, SQL Server, Entity Framework Core, ASP.NET Core Identity, and Azure deployment concepts.</p>
<p>The business workflow follows a request lifecycle from submission through review, assignment, progress tracking, resolution, and closure.</p>
